#. type: Plain text
#: original_texis/files.texi:2347
msgid ""
"To resize the image manually you can use the command "
"@code{image-transform-fit-to-window} bound to @kbd{s w} that fits the image "
"to both the window height and width.  To scale the image to a percentage of "
"its original size, use the command @code{image-transform-set-percent} bound "
"to @kbd{s p}.  To scale the image specifying a scale factor, use the command "
"@code{image-transform-set-scale} bound to @kbd{s s}.  To reset all "
"transformations to the initial state, use "
"@code{image-transform-reset-to-initial} bound to @kbd{s 0}, or "
"@code{image-transform-reset-to-original} bound to @kbd{s o}."
